::Rodimus Prime::

Rodimus got up from the rock, and began working on the Ark again.

::DrillBit::

DrillBit finished all his food, and drink. He walked to where KitKat,
Megatron and all were.
"Hey evrybody." He said.
He couldn't stop himself from looking streight at KitKat, with a amile.

OOC: If anyone want to fuss about how I knew where KK was. DrillBit was
just walking around looking, when he found the right room.
